Huawei is running a tech accessory sale from 15 – 21 July 2019, offering great discounts on awesome Huawei accessories. Accessories included in the deals are the Huawei Mini Speaker CM510 – available for only R1,299 – saving you R200, as well as FreeLace earphones for only R1,699 – saving you R300. Each sale product also comes with an additional free mystery gift. Deals are only available online, and are valid until stocks last. T’s and C’s apply. Huawei’s great Accessory Sale deals are listed below. For more information or to view the deals, visit the Huawei website. Available in orange and black. <img class="wp-image-313355 size-large aligncenter" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Freelace-640x217.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="217" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Freelace-640x217.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Freelace-600x203.jpg 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Freelace-768x260.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Freelace-1200x406.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> Available in green. <img class="wp-image-313357 size-large aligncenter" title="Click to enlarge" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Mini-speaker-640x217.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="217" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Mini-speaker-640x217.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Mini-speaker-600x203.jpg 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Mini-speaker-768x260.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Mini-speaker-1200x406.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> Available in red and grey. <img class="size-large wp-im